'''Shyamacharya''' or '''Kalakacharya I''' (c.247 BC - 151 BC) was a Jain monk.

==Life==
Shyamacharya or Kalakacharya I lived from c. 247 BC to 151 BC. He composed ''Prajnapaana Sutra'', an encyclopaedia of Jain tenets.{{sfn|Natubhai Shah|2004|p=47}}

